{"categories":["e-commerce"],"collections":"transactional","description":"Unlock the door to your online shopping experience with this vibrant, playful email template. The design is a delightful blend of blue and green hues, punctuated by charming illustrations and a light-hearted rose pattern. The key motif is a fun nod to its purpose - assisting you in retrieving your lost password. The colorful texture and sans serif typography add a touch of modernity, making it visually engaging and easy to read. Perfect for e-commerce platforms, this template strikes the right balance between fun and functionality. It ensures your password recovery process is as smooth and enjoyable as your shopping experience.","short_description":"Unlock your e-commerce experience with our vibrant, playful email template. Designed with charming illustrations, a blend of blue, green, and rose patterns, and a key motif for password recovery. Modern sans serif typography on a colorful texture enhances readability. Enjoy a fun, functional password recovery process.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/matteo-della-chiesa.jpg","description":"I've started to use Photoshop when I was 13. From 2009 to 2014, I've been a part of 5 Art Groups, doing Illustrations and Photo-manipulations, collaborating with over 150 Artists from all the Planet. In 2014, during my final school's exams, I've got my first Freelance Job at a Milan based Agency. Thanks to that first project, I started my Career as a Freelance Independent UI & Web Designer. Today, I help brands improve their online and digital presence, building usable, unique & beautiful products, mostly collaborating with Italian & US Agencies and Startups.","short_description":"","display_name":"Matteo Della Chiesa","id":"matteo-della-chiesa"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=